description: Learning how to model in 3D is a very important skill. You can 3D model, movies, video games and you can make CAD designs for 3D printers. If you know nothing about 3D modeling then this is the perfect place to start. In this short 1 hour tutorial series I am going to show you the basics of 3D modeling in blender. You can start learning a valuable skill today!
title: Learn 3D modeling in blender in 1 hour
